<%- include('partials/appheader') %>

<main>
  <header>
    <h1>Reviewer Dashboard</h1>
    <p>Welcome, <%= user.username %>! Here’s what’s happening on the platform.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Platform Overview</h2>
    <p>This section gives you insight into the current status of projects, users, and research activities.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Total projects: visible to reviewers</li>
      <li>Pending projects: under review</li>
      <li>Approved projects: successfully reviewed</li>
      <li>Rejected projects: those not meeting criteria</li>
      <li>Total users: researchers and admins included</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Recent Activity</h2>
    <p>Reviewers can monitor progress but do not modify content.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Researcher A submitted a project titled "AI in Healthcare"</li>
      <li>Project "Data Mining Techniques" was approved</li>
      <li>Project "Quantum Computing 101" is pending review</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <form action="/logout" method="get">
    <button type="submit">Logout</button>
  </form>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
